original_title: 2022 Tezos WNO: Gordon Ryan vs Felipe Pena
overview: Gordon Ryan takes on Felipe Pena in one of the biggest jiu-jitsu matches of all time!  No time limit, the only path to victory is submission, watch one of the most heated rivalries in the sport get settled at Tezos WNO!  The event goes down on August 7th from the Sports Academy at the Star in Frisco, Texas!
